steps.name: login to admin app

elements.name: Ordering for one vendor : Place order from Order edge

steps.name: user is on adminApp home page
Create a new Company "testCompany25Nov19" in adminApp
Create "testUser25Nov19" and assign "testCompany25Nov19" in adminApp
Login DE webApp with "testUser25Nov19"
Go to settings page
Create a new location "25Nov" with required basic and notification tab details
Verify the created location
Create a new vendor "US Foods"
Verify the created vendor "US Foods"
Edit vendor to add the Order notification E-mail addresses
Navigate to manage product list
Create a new product list as "myProductList" and assign to "25Nov"
Verify the created productList
Navigate to product list in manage items
Import a valid product list file
Verify the count of products imported from product list file
Switch to adminApp
Go to order guides in vendors in adminApp
Create a new order guide with file "USF GP" in adminApp
Verify the created order guide in adminApp
Switch to DE webApp
Go to Order Guides
Verify the created order guide in DE webApp
Add comparable for a product
Select quantity "10" to order
